cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent

Interface AgentController

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Controllable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseAgentController

    public interface AgentController
extends Controllable
    This interface represents a controller. The controller is a class that controls the bot. So the functions that might be necessary to that must be supplied. For example update, levelup etc.
    Author:
    Banzindun
